{"tid":14102,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"180蚊「抵抗失戀沖喜套餐」","createTime":"2016-11-30T11:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T15:00:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f0bd1a21f6703997f6e4a0bfa03e646e2653a1","tid":14102,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/190247_384716cdc65d2e434fc9fa20ca611323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F190247_384716cdc65d2e434fc9fa20ca611323.jpg&h=13dc3fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果不幸失戀的話，你會做甚麼呢？會否去吃一人的失戀餐呢？網民Nico Wong日前在 facebook群組「將軍澳」中上載了圖片，圖中顯示一家餐廳的餐牌，列出一個「抵抗失戀沖喜套餐」。套餐有蠔、牛舌、魚、羊或牛、雞翅膀及炒麵共6款食物，標明「流口水價$180」。貼文者表示感到「搞笑」，又問將軍澳街坊有否需要去試下。 <br />\n<br />\n不少網民看見此圖後都大感有趣，但不明白以上菜式如何可以抗失戀，有網民亦認為這個失戀餐算昂貴。有人亦認為如果點餐的時候大聲讀出這個名會感到尷尬，屆時全店人都會知道點餐者失戀。 <br />\n<br />\n網民有話說 <br />\n<br />\nHo Kui：嘩。180！？去餐廳食個靚扒 <br />\n<br />\nValkorion Vitiate Daz：竟然唔係每6秒6毫 <br />\n<br />\nMercy Ng ：介紹個朋友去食 <br />\n<br />\nCarson Leung：點解係抗失戀呢？？"},{"pid":"07adbb71e1126c2b5c7693cf5eb0ab31eee46a32","tid":14102,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ec8ae6ed0480c3f760d45142bcbc2d5d1d50e3","tid":14102,"uid":36744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"食完變雙失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錢都無埋"},{"pid":"5f41fec6819fec131e606956884098160461f51f","tid":14102,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:06:49.000Z","msg":"180<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=